<item>
            <title>[LU-13970] add an option to disable inode cache on Lustre client</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13970</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;By default inode is cached on Lustre client, to avoid OOM, an option like &lt;tt&gt;llite.&amp;#42;.inode_cache&lt;/tt&gt; can be added, when it&apos;s turned off, inode is immediately released on last iput().&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
